True if the person is adult, false otherwise.

-> birthdate (Date)
-> value (Integer)

if(
  and(
    a!isNotNullOrEmpty(ri!birthdate),
    a!isNotNullOrEmpty(ri!value)
  ),
  a!localVariables(
    local!diffYears: year(today()) - year(ri!birthdate),
    local!diffMonths: month(today()) - month(ri!birthdate),
    local!diffDays: day(today()) - day(ri!birthdate),
    if(
      local!diffYears > ri!value,
      true,
      if(
        local!diffYears < ri!value,
        false,
        if(
          local!diffMonths > 0,
          true,
          if(
            local!diffMonths < 0,
            false,
            if(local!diffDays >= 0, true, false)
          )
        )
      )
    )
  ),
  false
)

1. Nulls check (null, null) -> Test output matches the asserted output -> false (Boolean) -> Default
2. True test (01/24/2008, 18) -> Test output matches the asserted output -> true (Boolean)
3. False test (01/25/2008, 18) -> Test output matches the asserted output -> false (Boolean)
